        "timestamp": "2018-03-17 14:16:11.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nOne important note: I had to create a Jumbo commit, because the new policy examples and API have changed quite a bit from ECOMP version. This broke the unit tests (the process went as intended), so I had to touch quite a few items. This should address some code smells too (we had about 25 before these changes). Please review this soon. A majority of the changes relate to deleting old local policies.",
